    • Method Detail

      • filterCamps

        void filterCamps​(String filterString)
        Represents an interface that sets the filter bits of all the camps in a camp database in a manner defined by the implementor. Implementors should be associated with a camp database, and set the filter bits of the camps in the database according to whether it matches the filter string, or not.
        Parameters:
        filterString - The string to filter and find in the various camp information categories.
